      <h1>Playful Layers</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Semester 2 2023 · Individual Work · Columbia GSAPP</p>
      <p class="summary">
        Playful Layers explores how spatial boundaries can overlap, shift, and interact — producing playful conditions where public and private realms meet. The project investigates how adaptable partitions, textures, and transparencies can encourage new patterns of occupation and social interaction.
      </p>
